what is 2_3_4 Trees?!

A 2-3-4 Tree is an extension of a 2-3 Tree. Each node can have:

1 key â†’ 2-node

2 keys â†’ 3-node

3 keys â†’ 4-node (4-node is unique to 2-3-4 trees)


3 7 4 9 10 0 5 6 8 2 1

